snippet.textDisplay: Beautifully recited, Mashallah allahuma barik. May Allah bless you, Atif. Just one thing i need to point out, it seems like you didn't add Al-Ahad (which comes after Al-Wahid and before As-Samad), that means you have only recited 98 names of Allah. I apologise if i sound rude, but I appreciate you and everyone who worked hard to make this marvelous video. Thank you, i hope you look at this mistake. May Allah SWT keep us all safe from shaitan and keep us happy. Assalamualaikum.
